{"tid":655521,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好攰啦","createTime":"2018-05-06T14:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T15:31:58.000Z","uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43f61780eca8c18b75fe4c1e31e7686d0bd8e677","tid":655521,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:42:59.000Z","msg":"如果女朋友話&lsquo;女仔拍拖都係想有人就姐，唔係嘅話自己一個重好啦&rsquo; 你地會點諗？<br />\n<br />\n呢排佢同我都好大壓力 佢就發生左啲事 我就exam period 佢就成日發我脾氣 話我唔關心佢啊 唔體諒佢 我就衰唔忍得 哄下哄下忍唔住駁返佢 搞到唔到一日就鬧次大交 <br />\n<br />\n佢話我好自私靜係諗自己 仲成個細路咁<br />\n又話佢冇被照顧嘅感覺，以前不嬲有人照顧佢（講緊佢個ex)<br />\n<br />\n琴日我聽完個個句好hurt 講唔到點解 突然覺得冇曬自尊<br />\n<br />\n好撚自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6c362ab2728ed72ecce3cfa8dd6724cd455f00","tid":655521,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"唯一辦法<br />\n你做佢個ex <br />\n人只有失去先懂得珍惜🚬🚬🚬"},{"pid":"d0f64cc8a48b56daa867719ddd924beb72047c45","tid":655521,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c6c362ab2728ed72ecce3cfa8dd6724cd455f00","tid":655521,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"唯一辦法<br />\n你做佢個ex <br />\n人只有失去先懂得珍惜🚬🚬🚬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:56:43.000Z","msg":"我怕我失去先識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分唔到係我衰定佢衰"},{"pid":"e94be36d355d3ffe7773ddce05d33df537680add","tid":655521,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"咁都忍得，屎都食得"},{"pid":"1cd467f1f93990c65b8c525956c764d6588a3a91","tid":655521,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-06T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"中學雞預左散架啦"}]}